  "message": "Implement skills manifest.json tracking utilities\n\nAdd packages/cli/src/lib/manifest.ts with:\n- readManifest/writeManifest for persistent tracking\n- isJfpGenerated to check x_jfp_generated frontmatter\n- computeFileHash for detecting user modifications\n- checkSkillModification for safe update decisions\n- listInstalledSkills/getAllInstalledSkills for querying\n\nUpdates CLI tsconfig for proper type resolution.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
